data.oai_dc:dc: Data generated during qPCR validation of Yellow Perch SNP assay. Column headings: DNA concentration (ng/uL): final concentration of DNA in ng/uL added to validation assays, WA Ct: Cycle number at which Walleye DNA reached the amplification threshold when amplified with the Yellow Perch specific SNP assay, WB Ct: Cycle number at which White Bass DNA reached the amplification threshold when amplified with the Yellow Perch specific SNP assay, WP Ct: Cycle number at which White Perch DNA reached the amplification threshold when amplified with the Yellow Perch specific SNP assay, mean Ct: Average of all non-target predator Ct values when amplified with the Yellow Perch specific SNP assay, SD Ct: Standard Deviation of all non-target predator Ct values when amplified with the Yellow Perch specific SNP assay, SE Ct: Standard Error of all non-target predator Ct values when amplified with the Yellow Perch specific SNP assay
